  "text": "Initially, information visualization aided the identification of potential candidates for reverse engineering. A specialized tool, the workspace visualizer, developed by us for the visualization of instances of workspaces, was used for this purpose [CITATION_1] . An example of a so-called inter-workspace map, displaying relationships between workspaces, is shown in Figure 12 .",
